    "title": "Utawala na Nguvu ya Mungu Juu ya Mataifa Yote",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "utawala na nguvu ya mungu juu ya mataifa yote",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Katika nyakati za kale, watu wengi walidhani kila taifa lilikuwa na Mungu wake au miungu yake. Kwa mfano, mfalme wa Aramu alidhani miungu ya Israeli ilikuwa na nguvu tu milimani (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:23\">1 Wafalme 20:23</a>). Wakati hakimu Yeftha alipozungumzia mungu wa uongo Kemoshi akitoa ardhi kwa Waamoni, alikuwa akionyesha bado alifikiri kama watu waliokuwa wakiabudu miungu mingi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:24\">Waamuzi 11:24</a>).</p><p>Kinyume chake, nabii Amosi alijua kwamba ni Mungu pekee aliyewaleta Wafilisti kutoka Krete na Waaramu kutoka Kiri (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:7\">Amosi 9:7</a>). Mungu aliumba ulimwengu wote, si Israeli pekee (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:13\">4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:8\">5:8</a>). Kwa hivyo, alikuwa na haki ya kudai kwamba mataifa yatende kwa haki na huruma (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3-Amos1:2\">1:3–2:3</a>).</p><p>Kulikuwa na imani potofu ya kawaida miongoni mwa watu wa Yuda na Israeli kwamba licha ya dhambi zao, Mungu hatimaye angewaunga mkono kwa sababu ya agano lake nao (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:4\">Yeremia 7:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:1-Amos3:2\">Amosi 3:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:10\">9:10</a>). Walikosea kuamini kwamba &quot;Siku ya Bwana&quot; ilimaanisha uokoaji wa moja kwa moja kwao na maangamizi kwa maadui zao. Amosi alikabiliana moja kwa moja na hisia hii potofu ya upendeleo (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:7\">9:7</a>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:18-Amos5:20\">5:18–20</a>). Siku ya Bwana haingesamehe dhambi za Israeli. Badala yake, Mungu angeitumia kuwaadhibu.</p><p>Nafasi ya kipekee ya Israeli kati ya mataifa iliwapa jukumu kubwa zaidi. Wakati mataifa ya karibu yalipata adhabu kwa dhambi kali, Mungu aliadhibu Israeli kwa dhambi zao zote (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:2\">Amosi 3:2</a>). Agano Jipya linapanua wazo hili: &quot;Kila mtu ambaye amepewa mengi&quot; ana jukumu kubwa zaidi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:48\">Luka 12:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:1\">Yakobo 3:1</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:18\">Kutoka 15:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:8\">Kumbukumbu la Torati 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:11-1Chr29:12\">1 Mambo ya Nyakati 29:11–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:6\">2 Mambo ya Nyakati 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1-Ps2:12\">Zaburi 2:1–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps7:6-Ps7:8\">7:6–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:16\">10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:28\">22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps47:2\">47:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps83:18\">83:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1-Ps93:5\">93:1–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:19\">103:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:20-Dan2:21\">Danieli 2:20–21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:47\">47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34-Dan4:37\">4:34–37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos9:7\">Amosi 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">Mathayo 28:18–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24-Acts17:26\">Matendo 17:24–26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:17\">1 Timotheo 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:15\">6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:3-Rev15:4\">Ufunuo 15:3–4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:16\">19:16</a></p>",
